{"tid":637301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下月起深圳寄速遞 實名之外仲要查身份證","createTime":"2018-04-21T16:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T14:11:34.000Z","uid":62063,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab96e7eca8ee3934df4d35a8c29058ec5016ecf0","tid":637301,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"內地嚴控民眾一舉一動，下月起更進一步，嚴控民眾投寄速遞。下月起在深圳投寄速遞時，除要打開讓速遞員檢查投寄的物品外，還需要以實名填寫投寄單，更要出示證件，讓速遞員收集證件上的資料。<br />\n<br />\n國家郵政局、公安部、國安部去年已經要求實行投寄實名制，深圳已經配合實行，但有速遞企業發現，不少寄件人拒絕提供身份訊息，或是所提供的訊息不真確。為解決這問題，深圳市郵管局負責人稱，將在下月開始實行實名制。<br />\n有速遞企業透露新規定的執行細節：收件的傳遞員接到包裹後，即時開箱進行檢查，之後要求寄件人出示身份證，採集證件上的資料，上傳訊息到公司，之後要求寄件人如實填寫運單，不得簡化縮寫。<br />\n多間企業已經表示，已經對前線速遞員進行培訓，配合新規，同時表示將會確切落實新規。可是，不少網民擔心速遞企業或者洩漏他們的個人資料．「訊息不能保障，我怎麼敢用真名」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/003059_5f0e29f270dcd685eaa676e53d1c3852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F003059_5f0e29f270dcd685eaa676e53d1c3852.jpg&h=79d1c1fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47586f9b10dd4726bf220ca9ba439adb5fb8b6d1","tid":637301,"uid":61398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T16:34:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e069e7f046dcbf1537531ab34e798f33edc2eead","tid":637301,"uid":62063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"到時會唔會插贓嫁禍"},{"pid":"c9e9de6d9d49895a65bf26b1c2937107debd40cc","tid":637301,"uid":78385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:14:59.000Z","msg":"舊聞？一早已經係咁。<br />\n唔止拆盒，我寄隻電腦火牛，佢在出風口用電筒照入去。身份証要scan。"},{"pid":"a5c7f05e43c5c72f19b90aed83441e71c90ad9e0","tid":637301,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9e9de6d9d49895a65bf26b1c2937107debd40cc","tid":637301,"uid":78385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:14:59.000Z","msg":"舊聞？一早已經係咁。<br />\n唔止拆盒，我寄隻電腦火牛，佢在出風口用電筒照入去。身份証要scan。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:19:15.000Z","msg":"14小時前<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180421&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58099944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180421%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58099944&d=hxg47QoceM5mP1F6l8fP6gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=3a74dcbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180421%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58099944&h=bd9fb309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180421&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58099944</a>"},{"pid":"48ea6935e80fe25d5ea6462fcdd9a6faf957cd4e","tid":637301,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:22:32.000Z","msg":"幫我check哂佢全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354b2f391833f64d020bc426d7a781ce4265f333","tid":637301,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:46:51.000Z","msg":"發達！真正大數據！<br />\n<br />\n勁值錢！"},{"pid":"127476472135a2444502228f97b2090f3481078e","tid":637301,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}